# workshop

website for EnviBayes-INLA conference...under construction

the website can be accessed here <https://envibayesinla.github.io/workshop/>

things to do/add/check:

1.  **Welcome Civic Reception** – A warm welcome from the city, including a contribution towards a drink’s reception and a greeting from a member of the Lord Provost’s office (subject to availability; minimum 3 months’ notice required). The welcome civic reception can be held at the City Chambers and is a fantastic addition to a multi-day conference.
2.  **Free Impartial Accommodation Booking Support** – A one-stop shop for accommodation support near your conference venue. We can also provide general accommodation support services and contact sharing for smaller numbers.
